				<h2>Project Overview & Design</h2>
				<p>
					The idea was to create a minimal but aesthetically pleasing responsive site that would allow users to listen to each episode regardless of what device they are using. I definitely wanted to use some sort of card panel layout and have each episode assigned to it's own panel.
				</p>
				<h5><strong>Home Page</strong></h5>
				<%= image_tag "https://s3.amazonaws.com/danielcardeans-link/begin-fm/Home-2-1440x1452.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
				<br>
				<p>
					When a user clicks on the "Listen to episode" link I wanted them to be redirected to a page where they can play the episode and view all it's corresponding show notes. I wanted a simple color scheme. White card panels with a slightly gray background and a touch of purple purple scattered throughout.
				</p>
				<h5><strong>Listen to Episode Page</strong></h5>
